name: Swinghit
description: The goal is to complete each level without getting hit by the enemies and go to the next level with maximum number of stars. The game has no backstories the player has to simply play to get more stars in the level if they failed to complete the level then they can't proceed to next level. There are 48 levels in this game each with different gameplay and difficulty. Swinghit is made for Casual Gamers and hardcore gamers.
